===========================================================================
Distance matrix: Computing intercity time/distance using Google API 
===========================================================================
For a description:
> python scripts/distance_matrix.sh -h

See scripts/master_distance_matrix.sh for sequence of steps.

===========================================================================
Updating distances (such as adding cities)
===========================================================================
- go to results/domestic_distances
- add city to ${iso}_country_cities.txt
- run:
master_distance_matrix.sh domestic_distances
for only the relevant country.
